{"tid":1354083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上環果班真係condom仔","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T00:09:36.000Z","uid":154245,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bc1856b720094660e62715643a15e7ae2f711c02","tid":1354083,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:29:41.000Z","msg":"con你老母啊<br />\n有冇唸過依家對家送彈藥比我地啊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.無論你係藍黃絲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老弱婦孺</span> 黑幫與警察都照打<br />\n2.警察冇撚用唔會保護你，無論藍黃絲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老弱婦孺</span><br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察幫手協助黑幫秩序</span> 有埋片<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建制派議員</span>落場稱讚</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁做新子彈黎到，點解唔用<br />\n你上環係好嚴重<br />\n但係呢d彈藥如果可以好好善用<br />\n真係可以扭轉民義㗎<br />\n特別係淺藍<br />\n以下幾點做好，一定會越黎越多人對政府不滿<br />\n何況今次完全可以賴落建制派度<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.試著不要說何君堯與黑幫有關係</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試著說 建制派與黑幫有關係，叫佢哋打老弱婦孺</span></span><br />\n2.<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">試著不要說 黑警唔市民報案</span></span><br />\n試著說 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建制派與政府讓警察協助黑幫打市民</span></span><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">試著不要說上環condom仔</span></span><br />\n試著數 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依家警察與黑幫做事毫無分別，不用守法律，更不怕法律制裁，因為現在政府就是黑幫就是法律</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑幫=壞人 警察=好人<br />\n學生=壞人 老弱婦孺=無辜</span></span><br />\n呢個定律係好多人心目中都已成定律<br />\n依家係時候用d新名稱做文宣啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以前就話冇片，今次何君堯同八鄉個光頭送曬彈藥比我地</span></span><br />\n唔撚係唔用啊？<br />\n對面依家落錯棋啊<br />\n大大隻將軍擺係你只車面前啊<br />\n唔係唔撚食呀？<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"24b2171f5ef502d04172e64a6e7293283c6c0110","tid":1354083,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:33:44.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b653fd8a3c03270cf97e03b3421037abb01cd51c","tid":1354083,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:36:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1354083/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1354083/page/1?post=2</a>"},{"pid":"841e58ae03d823ce5a67831019ea0d8b437eaa96","tid":1354083,"uid":48981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"老實講 大家都知呢個新子彈作用可以好大，我地上環做condom有咩所謂"},{"pid":"0d2bb5e8612bc11493e0740f91c9f761df1e2603","tid":1354083,"uid":11929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:40:24.000Z","msg":"唔好再分化元朗同上環班手足<br />\n大家目標都係一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5bbab491906afe97240f1c8863eceafb5ed973","tid":1354083,"uid":154245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"841e58ae03d823ce5a67831019ea0d8b437eaa96","tid":1354083,"uid":48981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"老實講 大家都知呢個新子彈作用可以好大，我地上環做condom有咩所謂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"上環唔係做condom 係我地可以connect所有野一齊用<br />\n收政府皮"},{"pid":"edebd3a9b10cd96d48ea5b8812cc1c7afad8622d","tid":1354083,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:41:10.000Z","msg":"唔好比中共群眾鬥群眾分化計成功<br />\n<br />\n[反警黑大遊行] 朋友話，今舖要全港反警黑勾結大遊行，拉全建制派落水一齊玩完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351628</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"28cf268ab32eee72255c30336216df5780231025","tid":1354083,"uid":272010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"推,有用post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4864b7fcd8a408ed1795654f2e926dbaf14e1180","tid":1354083,"uid"